chuck c:/git/mandopi/eventTest.ck

instructions:
1-0, f1-12      play notes
backspace       stop
-,+             raise or lower next note by semitone
up, down arrow  raise or lower octave
r + 0-9         set reverb Level
k + c,a,g,e,d   set key

wii nunchuck:  (note, if having problems, push red button on uno to reset)
y-joystick      pitch bend

d + 0-9         set delay level -
c + 0-9         set chorus level
p + 0-9         set pan -
i + 0-9         set instrument
s + 0-9         set scale form
m               turn on/off multinote polyphony
numpad          start external file -
r-ctrl          enter sample mode.  use 1 or 2 to play samples.  ctrl again to exit. (how to stop?)
r-shft + 1-5    call preset 1-5
